### status: runtime-confirmed,recommended
### public: false
### authRequired: true
### sessionAuthRequired: false
### tenantScopedHeadersRequired: true
### destructive: false
### requiresTenantHeaders: true
### llmOperational: true
### protectedContract: false
### referenceOnly: false
### runtimeRecordConfirmed: true
### selectorConfirmed: true
### publishedBackendConfirmed: true
### knownPublishedFailure: false
### accessMode: auth-light
### selectionGuidance: safe-first-auth-light
### note: This example does not require login, cookies, or bearer auth.
### note: authRequired is a legacy compatibility alias here; read sessionAuthRequired and tenantScopedHeadersRequired instead.
### note: Accepted now on the published backend: Accept plus Content-Type for POST bodies.
### note: Default recommended stable scoped trio: X-Tenant-ID, X-User-ID, X-Env.

@baseUrl = https://praxis-api-quickstart.onrender.com
@tenantId = demo
@userId = example-user
@envId = public

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/human-resources/vw-ranking-reputacao/options/filter?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-User-ID: {{userId}}
X-Env: {{envId}}

< ../../payloads/views/vw_ranking_reputacao_filter_basic.json
